DESCRIPTION:Annually\, the HAND department hosts this gathering of neighbor
 hoods as an opportunity to network\, share\, and celebrate neighborhood acc
 omplishments. Neighborhood representatives and members of community organiz
 ations assemble on the terraces under the trees in front of City Hall for f
 ellowship and fun. \n\nHeld at the Bloomington Community Farmers Market\, i
 n conjunction with Harvest for the World.
