DESCRIPTION:Animal shelters across the country will soon be full of pregnan
 t cats\, newborn and young kittens. It is times like these we rely on our c
 ommunity members to help us care for this vulnerable population of shelter 
 animals.\n\n\nBecoming a foster parent for a shelter animal is one of the m
 ost rewarding ways to share your time! Join our team of superheroes and hel
 p us continue our life saving work! \n\nThis training is open to the public
  and new fosters can be oriented at the time of training. \n\nFor questions
  regarding this training or the foster program\, please contact Robyn Peffi
 nger at peffingr@bloomington.in.gov
LAST-MODIFIED:20250821T130706Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Neonatal Kitten Foster Training
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
