DESCRIPTION:<h2><b>Come support us!</b></h2><p>Have you always wanted to pa
 int the perfect picture of your beloved pet? Now is your chance! Join us at
  Switchyard Brewing for the chance to drink great beer and raise money for 
 the City of Bloomington Animal Care and Control.&nbsp\;</p><p>Each painter 
 will get the 2 different painting styles to work with</p><p>Option 1: Tradi
 tional style.&nbsp\;</p><p>Option 2: Pop art style. Think bright colors (An
 dy Warhol)&nbsp\;</p><p><strong><b>Sessions:&nbsp\;</b></strong></p><p>Sess
 ion 1: 11am - 2pm&nbsp\;</p><p>Session 2: 3pm - 6pm</p><p><strong><b>Ticket
 s</b></strong></p><p>Tickets are $45/person and are required to attend this
  event. Please arrive on time and note that photos of your pet must be subm
 itted to the instructor prior to the event!&nbsp\;</p><p>Additionally $25 o
 f your ticket will be donated to City of Bloomington Animal Care and Contro
 l&nbsp\;</p><p><strong><b>PET PHOTO submissions:</b></strong></p><p>Please 
 submit a photo of your pet via email to our instructor\, Zach\, at zachlowe
 .gallery@gmail.com BEFORE Saturday\, Jan 28th. Please include your full nam
 e and 3-5 high-quality photographs of your pet. Please also include "Bloomi
 ngton" in the subject line. 1 pet per canvas.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250821T130652Z
LOCATION:Switchyard Brewing Company\, 419 N Walnut St\, Bloomington\, IN 47
 404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Paint Your Pet!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
