DESCRIPTION:<br>Join Mayor Kerry Thomson for her Traveling Office Hours on 
 Tuesday\, October 8 from 2-4 p.m. at Crumble Coffee and Bakery\, 1567 S Pia
 zza Dr. This is your chance to engage with the Mayor in an informal setting
 \, ask questions\, receive updates on local initiatives\, and share any fee
 dback you may have.<br><br>Why attend?<br><br>To best serve our community\,
  we need to stay connected to it. This means prioritizing listening to the 
 people of Bloomington and understanding their needs. These Traveling Office
  Hours provide a relaxed and personal environment for residents to interact
  with Mayor Thomson.<br><br>• Follow this link to register: <a href="https:
 //calendar.app.google/9Utukew1Pog17LpX8?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR1Xlk1Rsy
 0Oh-UsohzBAP3kMG0c3YkEnq98WeYMb3wmMQcommpZw0RXgsg_aem_TLKPoxFlBqnwBxcG9CPXz
 w" target="_blank">https://calendar.app.google/9Utukew1Pog17LpX8</a><br><br
 >• Click on Tuesday\, October 8\, select a 15-minute timeslot\, fill out th
 e form\, and let us know what you’d like to chat about.<br><br>• Alternativ
 ely\, you can all the Office of the Mayor at 812-349-3406 and we’ll get you
  registered by phone.<br><br>Don’t miss this fantastic opportunity to conne
 ct with Mayor Thomson\, enjoy a cup of coffee\, and make your voice heard. 
 We look forward to seeing you there!<br><br>Please note: If you have alread
 y participated in a one-on-one session\, we kindly ask that you waitlist yo
 urself so that others have an opportunity to meet with Mayor Thomson.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250820T203427Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Traveling Office Hours with Mayor Kerry Thomson
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
