DESCRIPTION:Join Mayor Kerry Thomson for her Traveling Office Hours on Tues
 day\, March 4 from 11:30 a.m. until 1:30 p.m. at Bloomington Farm Stop Coll
 ective\, 902 W Kirkwood Ave. This is your chance to engage with the Mayor i
 n an informal setting\, ask questions\, receive updates on local initiative
 s\, and share any feedback you may have. Appointments will be scheduled in 
 15-minute intervals to ensure everyone has an opportunity to connect. <b><a
  href="https://ootm.schedulebloomington.com/farmstop2025">Please register o
 nline in advance</a></b> or contact the Mayor's Office at 812-349-3406 to b
 ook an appointment.<br><br><b><i>Why attend?</i></b><br><br>To best serve o
 ur community\, we need to stay connected to it. This means prioritizing lis
 tening to the people of Bloomington and understanding their needs. These Tr
 aveling Office Hours provide a relaxed and personal environment for residen
 ts to interact with Mayor Thomson.<br><br>Please note: If you've already co
 nnected with Mayor Thomson during Traveling Office Hours\, please refrain f
 rom registering at this time to provide others with the opportunity.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250820T203434Z
