DESCRIPTION:\nAnimal shelters across the country will soon be full of pregn
 ant cats\, newborn and young kittens. It is times like these we rely on our
  community members to help us care for this vulnerable population of shelte
 r animals.\n\nBecoming a foster parent for a shelter animal is one of the m
 ost rewarding ways to share your time! Join our team of superheroes and hel
 p us continue our life saving work! \n\n***This training is open to the pub
 lic and new fosters can be oriented at the time of training.***\n\nFor ques
 tions regarding this training or the foster program\, please contact Robyn 
 Peffinger at <a href="mailto:peffingr@bloomington.in.gov" target="_blank">p
 effingr@bloomington.in.gov</a>
