DESCRIPTION:Paint your pet is back at Switchyard!<br><br>Have you always wa
 nted to paint the perfect picture of your beloved pet? Now is your chance! 
 Join us at Switchyard Brewing for the chance to drink great beer and raise 
 money for a great cause!<br>$﻿20 of each ticket will be donated to City of 
 Bloomington Animal Care and Control.<br><br>H﻿ow it works:<br>Y﻿ou will rec
 eive a canvas with your pet sketched out (photo submission details below). 
 You will then be guided through a detailed step by step process how to pain
 t your specific pet . You will be limited to 1 pet per canvas.<br>Y﻿ou can 
 paint your pet in 1 of 2 styles<br>1﻿. Pop art style (think vibrant colors\
 , Any Warhol)<br>2﻿. Traditional style\, painting your pet true to their co
 lors.<br><br>PET PHOTO submissions:<br>Please submit a photo of your pet vi
 a email to our instructor\, Zach\, at zachlowe.gallery@gmail.com BEFORE Aug
 ust 12th. Please include your full name and 3-5 high-quality photographs of
  your pet. Please also include "Bloomington" in the subject line.<br><br><a
  href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/paint-your-pet-benefitting-city-of-bloo
 mington-animal-care-and-control-tickets-686993775877?aff=oddtdtcreator&amp\
 ;fbclid=IwAR3JAvjhl4p6c4plLvuQgItXTeODsbFp_f0-va1ntfst-CD61qEqPQrvZOI">http
 s://www.eventbrite.com/e/paint-your-pet-benefitting-city-of-bloomington-ani
 mal-care-and-control-tickets-686993775877?aff=oddtdtcreator&amp\;fbclid=IwA
 R3JAvjhl4p6c4plLvuQgItXTeODsbFp_f0-va1ntfst-CD61qEqPQrvZOI</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250821T130653Z
LOCATION:Switchyard Brewing Company\, 419 N Walnut St\, Bloomington\, IN 47
 404\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Paint Your Pet Event at Switchyard Brewing Company
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
