DESCRIPTION:<br>Join Mayor Kerry Thomson for her Traveling Office Hours on 
 Tuesday\, January 28 from 11:30 a.m. until 1:30 p.m. at Hopscotch Coffee &a
 mp\; Kitchen\, 235 W Dodds St #102. This is your chance to engage with the 
 Mayor in an informal setting\, ask questions\, receive updates on local ini
 tiatives\, and share any feedback you may have one-on-one.<br><br>Appointme
 nts will be scheduled in 15-minute intervals to ensure everyone has an oppo
 rtunity to connect. You must register in advance.<br><br>To book an appoint
 ment\, please visit <a href="http://ootm.schedulebloomington.com/jan25?fbcl
 id=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2jDtYNOIBg0KBGAWruFddxbsG_j-9P-f0nLluo6-A-wPBXPja0ZI
 5d9So_aem_sHMLJWJz1Oji-1hW1lF5JQ" target="_blank">ootm.schedulebloomington.
 com/jan25</a> or call the Office of the Mayor at 812-349-3406.<br><br><b>Wh
 y attend?<br><br></b><br>To best serve our community\, we need to stay conn
 ected to it. This means prioritizing listening to the people of Bloomington
  and understanding their needs. These Traveling Office Hours provide a rela
 xed and personal environment for residents to interact with Mayor Thomson.<
 br><br>Please note: If you've already connected with Mayor Thomson during T
 raveling Office Hours\, please refrain from registering at this time to pro
 vide others with the opportunity.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250820T203432Z
