DESCRIPTION:\nJoin us for an evening of fun as we celebrate Be Kind to Anim
 als Week. \nChildren of all ages are invited to the City of Bloomington Ani
 mal Shelter on Tuesday\, May 9th from 5:30-7:30 p.m. \n\nEngagement opportu
 nities will include our Book Buddies program and Toy/Enrichment building st
 ations. Children may participate in both activities and are encouraged to d
 o so! \nBook Buddies are asked to bring their favorite book\, snuggle up wi
 th a shelter animal and read aloud for 15-30 minutes. \n\nToy/Enrichment bu
 ilding stations will be set up in our Education Room where children can bui
 ld enrichment items for shelter animals. Shelter dogs will be present to su
 pervise the building process. \n\nChildren must have a guardian with them a
 t all times. Children may not be dropped off for the event. The event is dr
 op in and families may join anytime between 5:30-7:30 pm.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250821T130653Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Be Kind to Animals Week After-Hours Celebration 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
