DESCRIPTION:<br><p><strong><b>Come get creative with us!</b></strong></p><b
 r><h2>About this event</h2><br><br><br><h2><b>Come support us!</b></h2><p>H
 ave you always wanted to paint the perfect picture of your beloved pet? Now
  is your chance! Join us at Switchyard Brewing for the chance to drink grea
 t beer and raise money for the City of Bloomington Animal Care and Control.
 &nbsp\;</p><p>Each painter will get the 2 different painting styles to work
  with</p><p>Option 1: Traditional style.&nbsp\;</p><p>Option 2: Pop art sty
 le. Think bright colors (Andy Warhol)&nbsp\;</p><p><strong><b>Sessions:&nbs
 p\;</b></strong></p><p>Session 1: 11am - 2pm&nbsp\;</p><p>Session 2: 3pm - 
 6pm</p><p><strong><b>Tickets</b></strong></p><p>Tickets are $45/person and 
 are required to attend this event. Please arrive on time and note that phot
 os of your pet must be submitted to the instructor prior to the event!&nbsp
 \;</p><p>Additionally $25 of your ticket will be donated to City of Bloomin
 gton Animal Care and Control&nbsp\;</p><p><strong><b>PET PHOTO submissions:
 </b></strong></p><p>Please submit a photo of your pet via email to our inst
 ructor\, Zach\, at zachlowe.gallery@gmail.com BEFORE Friday\, September 23.
  Please include your full name and 3-5 high-quality photographs of your pet
 . Please also include "Bloomington" in the subject line. 1 pet per canvas.<
 /p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250821T130648Z
LOCATION:Switchyard Brewing Company\, 419 N Walnut St\, Bloomington\, IN 47
 404\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Paint Your Pet at Switchyard Brewing Company
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
